  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Scout-Nin Keyword: Specialized When you would make a weapon/unarmed attack or cast a jutsu that requires an attack roll, you can expend one Superiority Die, recording the result.</p><p> Select a number of creatures within 5 feet of your first target.</p><p> Add your Superiority Die to the first attack roll of the jutsu cast.</p><p> On a hit, the initial target and all selected targets, suffer the damage of that attack as if they were the original target.</p><p> This does not inflict any effects the jutsu would normally inflict to a creature hit by it, to chosen adjacent creatures.</p>",
